subject: Basketball
College Athletics
Basketball (College)
lead_paragraph: Shabazz Muhammad scored 20 points and No. 11 U.C.L.A. made enough free throws late to beat Georgia on Tuesday night in the consolation game of the Legends Classic at Barclays Center.
